WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.735 --> 00:00:04.064
Control sensitive data before AI sees it. This short demo uses the public website and playground surfaces, with safe sample data only.

2
00:00:04.694 --> 00:00:07.495
Buyers can test the control model immediately. The playground shows the masking path before anyone needs to book a live call.

3
00:00:08.493 --> 00:00:11.198
Start with a regulated workflow prompt. This sample includes an IBAN and payment card so the masking behavior is obvious.

4
00:00:11.996 --> 00:00:15.498
Original and sanitized outputs sit side by side. The raw prompt remains visible for review while the outbound version uses typed tokens.

5
00:00:16.235 --> 00:00:19.338
Teams can inspect what was found. Entity type, matched text, and confidence context make the control easier to review.

6
00:00:24.255 --> 00:00:27.759
Reversible mode creates scoped demo tokens. That explains the restore model without sending raw identifiers through normal AI traffic.

7
00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:31.962
Use the video before a sales call. It gives a buyer enough context to decide whether a live walkthrough is worth their time.
